text: The Ingénieurs et scientifiques de France (IESF), named before Conseil national des Ingénieurs et Scientifiques de France (CNISF), is an association, created in 1992 in order to be representative in France and abroad of French engineers and scientists.Création du Conseil national des ingénieurs et scientifiques de France It is composed by former students associations and societies.Historique It is managed by Frédéric Misheletti.Le conseil d'administration ==References== ==Further reading== * Official website Category:Education in France
